%% 3.2.4 Delete Account (Staff) — sequence (layered)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Super Admin
    participant UI as UI (/accounts)
    participant UC as Controller (UserController)
    participant US as Service (UserService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository User)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Actor->>UI: Confirm Delete Account
    UI->>UC: DELETE /api/User/Delete/{id}
    UC->>US: DeleteUserAsync — Status DISABLED
    US->>Repo: Update
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE
    UC-->>UI: 200
    UI-->>Actor: Toast — row fades out

    Note over UI,DB: Staff logged in elsewhere — JWT valid until expiry; mọi API có kiểm tra Status sẽ từ chối.
